text: The cave spikethumb frog (Plectrohyla tecunumani) is a frog that lives in Guatemala. Scientists have only seen it three times. It lives very high above sea level. Scientists saw it in the Sierra de Cuchumatanes in western Guatemala at 3200 to 3395 meters above sea level. ==References== Category:Frogs of North America
title: Plectrohyla tecunumani
